{"tid":1778732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」呢個深黃歌手啱啱出左新歌 大家諗住點懲罰佢？","createTime":"2019-12-11T07:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T07:32:46.000Z","uid":341790,"like":72,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"5539b349146d0e2262d42050f2c10991d3f289a1","tid":1778732,"uid":341790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:18:26.000Z","msg":"佢就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">符家浚</span></span>喇！ (唔係篤波嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n一直跟開佢IG都知佢有表態，但無乜人講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱見到佢突發出歌，仲要咁<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">深黃</span></span>，決定要做打手幫佢開個post，等多啲人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AiATho-NOgo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAiATho-NOgo&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwgKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=0be8381a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AiATho-NOgo</a><br />\n<br />\n《絶不棄權》<br />\n<br />\n曲：黃安弘<br />\n詞：詩詞<br />\n編：黃安弘<br />\n監：黃安弘<br />\n唱：符家浚<br />\n<br />\n誰能料到天色變化 舊有的倒下<br />\n誰能料到轟一聲 你已沒法講話<br />\n誰料美麗年華 會陌生得可怕<br />\n如最壞一刻光臨 物極而反 也接近<br />\n<br />\n*想過成王敗寇要投降<br />\n所費不枉 有夢 哪會後悔苦幹<br />\n誰會退縮 翻身再闖<br />\n<br />\n假設明日被世界遺忘<br />\n只要今天 曾以這身軀抵抗 流血汗<br />\n連繫過 是兩手 而連結不放*<br />\n<br />\n誰能料到心中會怕 為了講真話<br />\n誰能料到烽煙中 已太習慣驚訝<br />\n誰料到在未來 這歷史怎演化<br />\n如綜合一點精華 上善如水 智慧剩下<br />\n<br />\nRepeat*<br />\n<br />\n當你曾流淚哪會投降<br />\n所費不枉 有夢 見證現世 一改既往<br />\n存下昐望<br />\n無懼怕 怎麼去檔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">假設明日被世界遺忘<br />\n相信今天 曾以這身軀抵抗 流下血汗<br />\n憑着信念發光 時代正開創<br />\n期待有日說聲 猶幸你在旁</span></span><br />\n<br />\n又有邊個會諗到，5年前《自動棄權》嘅下集，居然會係一隻抗爭歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港本土歌手 一定要大大力支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3596f1eca4e6d3c9f373319446582c3722a872ce","tid":1778732,"uid":341790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:20:07.000Z","msg":"幫手推 p牌仔推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每個手足都要支持！"},{"pid":"a56fe06f632edc2103cb0f9de015bf82e7241c6c","tid":1778732,"uid":341790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:23:24.000Z","msg":"推唔郁照推 1/10"},{"pid":"7b18764a856928301e104ba1c9aeb798e99376b8","tid":1778732,"uid":341790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:23:36.000Z","msg":"推唔郁照推 2/10"},{"pid":"9ad21dd781d207c92ae23dffff8ba9672411a54f","tid":1778732,"uid":341790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"推唔郁照推 3/10"},{"pid":"9cfd962acc0b422d13ed67b18bceff8ea9366ebc","tid":1778732,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:24:01.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"95cb72ecd2da581211f0012274b99bc2ced40708","tid":1778732,"uid":218183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T07:24:24.000Z","msg":"推撚爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n願永光、人話同煲底之約都上唔到吒咤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"660624e32deb6bcd1dd4bb8c1b07eb7523279d41","tid":1778732,"uid":341790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cfd962acc0b422d13ed67b18bceff8ea9366ebc","tid":1778732,"uid